stories.title: Namibia, PNG secure ODI status after wins over HK and Oman
stories.subTitle: WCL Division Two, day five, Windhoek
stories.seoTitle: Namibia, PNG secure ODI status after wins over HK and Oman
stories.summary: Canada needed to restrict USA to 211 if they were to regain ODI status, but USA's last-wicket pair denied them with a boundary in the final over
stories.byline: The Report by Peter Della Penna in Windhoek
